INKANTOLO yeMantshi eMnambithi imgwebe udilikajele umsolwa otholwe enecala lokudlwengula ingane eneminyaka eyisishiyagalolunye. U-Atiso Stenly Mofokeng (30), kuthiwa wabiza  umgilwa ngo-Agasti 2020, e-Elandslaagte, ezenza umuntu ofuna ukumthuma ugwayi esitolo. Umsolwa kubikwa ukuthi wabamba umgilwa ngenkani,  wamkhumula izimpahla ayezigqokile wamdlwengula. Ngenkathi enza lokhu, kubikwa ukuthi wayembambe umlomo ngoba emvimba ukuthi angamemezi. Ngemuva kokugila ingane, kubikwa ukuthi wayitshela ukuthi ayigqoke. Umgilwa kubikwa ukuthi wafika kubo watshela ugogo wakhe okumehlele. Okhulumela iNational Prosecuting Authority KwaZulu-Natal  uNkk Natasha Kara, uthe umsolwa wakhonjwa ngumgilwa ngaphambi kokuthi avalelwe ngamaphoyisa esitokisini. “UMofokeng oqale waliphika icala enkantolo, kubikwa ukuthi kwagcina ngokuthi alivume ngenkathi seliqulwa. Akekho owabhadama umsolwa endaweni yesigameko ngokwesitatimende esathulwa enkantolo kodwa kunomfundi wesikole sasendaweni, owaqinisekisa ukuthi wambona ephuma esigangeni nomgilwa,” kubeka uNkk Kara. Isitatimende esethulwe ngumshushisi  uNkk Ashina Devi Singh,  siveza ukuthi umgilwa  bese ehlezi ehlalele ovalweni ngemuva kwesehlo. Ugogo wakhe oneminyaka engu-73, kubikwa ukuthi nguye obesehlezi emphelezela njalo ekuseni  uma eya esikoleni. Kubikwa ukuthi isimo sikanina kamgilwa , sigcine sintekenteke ngenxa yalesi sigameko, esenzeka esanda kushonelwa ngumyeni wakhe. Kubikwa ukuthi kugcine ngokuthi ashiye kulesi sifundazwe njengoba esezinze eGoli nomgilwa osefunda khona. Umshushisi uphinde wazisa inkantolo ukuthi umsolwa uthinteka nasecaleni lokugqekeza nelokushaya. UMqondisi wabaShushisi KwaZulu- Natal u-Advocate Elaine Zungu , uthe sikhulu isikhalo emphakathini ngamacala athinta ukuhlukunyezwa kwezingane. “Yize uMbuso ubungenayo imiphumela yolibofuzo, ubufakazi obuqanda ikhanda bofakazi yibo obuqinisekise isenzo sikamsolwa. Sinxusa amalungu omphakathi ukuthi ahlezi eqaphile ngaso sonke isikhathi,” kubeka u-Advocate Zungu. 